  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为IoT工业边缘节点的固件更新流程画一个Git分支图。核心场景是main分支和develop分支之间的双向合并，体现持续集成时的来回同步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "develop",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，双向合并是指main合并到develop、同时develop也合并回main？另外标题我想用\"Two-way merges (IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode)\"来明确场景，可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "main",
        "develop",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，标题没问题。流程上先让main有个初始commit，然后从main切出develop分支，develop上做一次提交，接着main去合并develop——这是第一次单向同步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "develop",
        "commit",
        "checkout",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把基础结构搭好：main初始commit，切出develop并提交，然后checkout回main完成第一次merge。接下来develop要合并main对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "develop",
        "commit",
        "checkout",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，develop checkout之后合并main，这样两边就同步了。然后develop再提交一个新commit，最后main再次合并develop，形成完整的双向循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "main",
        "checkout",
        "merge",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，develop合并main后提交，再切回main做最终merge。这样总共三次merge操作，develop上有两次提交，能体现边缘节点固件在双分支间的持续同步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "main",
        "merge",
        "commit",
        "checkout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，develop在第二次merge main之后应该有个commit，但我看现在develop的第二个commit画在了合并之前？顺序需要调整，应该是先merge main，再commit，最后main来合并develop。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "main",
        "merge",
        "commit",
        "checkout"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，develop checkout后先merge main，然后commit，最后main checkout回来merge develop。现在时序对了：main←develop→同步→develop←main→新提交→main←develop。",
      "elements_involved": [
